          </span>
          <span class="footer__sep">·</span>
          <span>MIT License</span>
        </div>
        <div class="footer__right">
          <span>v0.3.1</span>
          <span class="footer__sep">·</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/vncsleal/scheml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/vncsleal/scheml</a>
        </div>
